Package: tsml.cara.rct
Type: Package
Title: Targeted Sequential Minimum Loss Covariate-Adjusted Response-Adaptive RCT design and statistical inference
Version: 0.0.4
Date: 2016-09-16
Author: Antoine Chambaz
Maintainer: Antoine Chambaz <achambaz@u-paris10.fr>
Description: The package allows to simulate easily a targeted sequential minimum loss covariate-adjusted response-adaptive randomized clinical trial design sampling and that statistical inference of the average treatment effect or mean reward of the optimal treatment rule
License: GPL
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Depends: R (>= 2.9.0), R.utils (>= 1.4.1), glmnet (>= 1.9-5)
Imports: R.methodsS3, R.oo
Suggests: SuperLearner (>= 2.0), e1071 (>= 1.5.24), randomForest (>= 4.5-35), polspline (>= 1.1.4), gam (>= 1.03)
